    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just a ghost lately. like i'm just going through the motions of being a person, but there's nothing actually inside. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back, it's just a performance for everyone else. i'm not even here anymore.",
