      "content": "the professional stuff feels like just another role i have to play. \"patient,\" \"someone trying to get better,\" \"someone who follows instructions.\" i'm so tired of the script. honestly, sometimes i look at the exit and it feels like the only real thing left. like, if there's no one actually home in here, why should the lights stay on?",
